schemaVersion: 1
id: physics-experiments-root
name: Physics Experiments
kind: root
version: 0.1.0
description: >
  Five interactive, self-contained simulations of classic physics experiments —
  double-slit, pendulum wave, projectile motion, wave interference, and the
  brachistochrone race. Vanilla JS + Canvas 2D, zero build step, runs entirely
  in the browser. Each experiment is a full-screen Cabinet app you can open
  from the sidebar.
entry: index.md
